Forecast presentation acceptable, but worse than  Windguru, especially on small screen as multi-day graph limited to wind (no temperature, rain, clouds, pressure). Wave prediction as bad as Meteo Consult in Western Mediterranean. Favorites presented in the order that they were selected, therefore it is possible, if a list is made before entering the spots, to have them in desired order (that is better than Windguru), but it is not possible to change this order. Too much space wasted at top of small screen, for little useful information. Super-forecast limited to less than 72 hours. No documented procedure to save the favorites in order to use them on a different device. Maps require the dreaded Google Play Services, but forecasts can be accessed even if this monster is not installed. Not available for Android 2.3. Overall acceptable app if the user needs to have the predictions available shortly after the forecast run and wants to avoid data wasted on adds.
